<% provide(:title, "Help") %>
<div class="white_belt"><h1><%= yield(:title) %></h1></div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 white_wall">
    <li><a href="#signup"><%= t :ユーザー情報を登録 %></a></li>
    <li><a href="#login"><%= t :ログイン %></a></li>
    <li><a href="#test"><%= t :テストを受ける %></a></li>
    <li><a href="#create_test"><%= t :テストを作る %></a></li>
    <li><a href="#grade"><%= t :成績を見る %></a></li>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-7 white_block">
    <div id="signup"><h4><li><%= t :ユーザー情報を登録 %></li></h4></div><br>
    <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag 'signup.png', size: '600x350'%>
    </div>
    <br>
    Click "⇨New user? Let's sign up!"<br>
    And please enter your name, email-address, password on the signup page.<br>
    If you click "Signup" button, the confirmation email will be sent to your address.<br>
    Signup will be completed, if you click the email link.<br>
    <br>
    <div id="login"><h4><li><%= t :ログイン %></h4></li></div><br>
    <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag 'login.png', size: '600x350'%>
    </div>
    <br>
    Enter your email address and password, and click "Log in" on the top page.<br>
    <br>
    <div id="test"><h4><li><%= t :テストを受ける %></h4></li></div><br>
    <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag 'Testlist.jpg', size: '600x300'%>
    </div>
    <br>
    After logged in, click "test" on the side menu.<br>
    Then you can see the tests lit on the right side of the page.<br>
    If you click The title of tests, you will see the taking test page.<br>
    <br>
    <div id="create_test"><h4><li><%= t :テストを作る %></li></h4></div><br>
    <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag 'Create.jpg', size: '600x300'%>
    </div>
    <br>
    Ahter logged in, click "Create" on the side menu.<br>
    Enter the category and title.<br>
    Then you can see the test title on the right side.<br>
    Please click "question", next.<br>
    <br>
    Please enter the question on the left side form.<br>
    Click "create question".<br>
    And you will see the question on the right side.<br>
    Then, click "create selects".<br>
    <br>
    Please enter the problem options on the left side of the page.<br>
    If the option is correct answer, check the check box.<br>
    If the option is incorrect answer, leave it unchecked and click "Create selects".<br>
    <br>
    <div id="grade"><h4><li><%= t :成績を見る %></h4></li></div><br>
    <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag 'grade.jpg', size: '600x250'%>
    </div>
    <br>
    Click "Grade" to see the results of the tests you have taken in the past.<br>
    A list of the tests you took will appear on the right side of the page.<br>
    And click the test you want to check.<br>
    <br>
  </div>
</div>
